{"type": "article", "id": 18667, "title": "朗姆酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-08T07:42:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104215yHsxafB3voCUrqt9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tStranger &amp; Stranger 是英国专门设计酒类包装的工作室，他们为 Kraken 设计的朗姆酒运用了海怪的元素。陶瓷瓶身上的海怪做出浮雕的效果，立刻让这瓶酒有了神秘感，有点黑暗童话的感觉，让人忍不住去触摸。相应的瓶口旁边设计了两个圆圈把手，配合乳白色的瓶身，很复古。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071042141tXfyGK07ze2AEI3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.24349442\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104215PpGQ6TEXcwdZv2bI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66728625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104215C2XKZhMQrsLHG7TW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.90334572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}